Ceiling fans in all the right places. Primary bedroom offers a full bathroom with upgraded modern cabinetry, raised dual vanity & sinks, oversized soaker tub & a walk-in closet. Enjoy your private backyard retreat with the cozy upgraded covered patio, built in speakers, well-laid pavers, and artificial turf that create an ideal space for relaxation & entertainment year round.
